  {
    "id": 136,
    "properties": {
      "text": "This aligns with Nietzsche's perspectives on embracing life's struggles, hardships, and the harsh realities of existence rather than shying away from them. His concept of \"amor fati\" (love of one's fate) is about affirmatively willing and accepting all consequences."
    },
